# Always build `dist/`

After any implementation that changes the app (UI, logic, i18n, config, version), run a production build before finishing so `dist/` stays current:

```bash
npm run build
```

On Windows, if `npm` is not on PATH, use WSL:

```bash
wsl -e bash -lc 'cd /mnt/e/Cursor-Project/FO-Simulator && npm run build'
```

Do this without waiting for the user to ask, unless the request was plan/review only with no code changes.
